videos.description: Lonzo Ball explains what the Lakers did well to end the Rockets' 14-game winning streak and praises Kyle Kuzma after his 38-point effort.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Lonzo proud of how Lakers closed out Rockets) 2017/12/20

videos.headline: Lonzo proud of how Lakers closed out Rockets

videos.description: James Harden says the Lakers played with a lot of confidence and admits that no matter who they're playing, it's difficult to overcome a 22-point deficit.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Interview (Harden gives the Lakers credit, especially from 3-point land) 2017/12/20

videos.headline: Harden gives the Lakers credit, especially from 3-point land

videos.description: Rockets head coach Mike D'Antoni says that he thought they'd never lose but is excited and ready to start another winning streak. D'Antoni also comments on Chris Paul's injury, saying it's an adductor strain and his return is unknown.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Press Conference (D'Antoni: 'Man I thought we'd never lose') 2017/12/20

videos.headline: D'Antoni: 'Man I thought we'd never lose'
